snippet.title: Project Century World Premiere Trailer from The Game Awards 2024
snippet.description:
Watch the Project Century World Premiere Trailer from The Game Awards 2024. Live from Peacock Theater in Los Angeles, join Geoff Keighley and the video game industry for a celebration of the year's best -- and a look at what's next.

Subscribe to Watch more The Game Awards:  http://bit.ly/tga18sub
